room_title: Escape room "Speakeasy" by EscapeQuest in Chicago
room_description: It's 1920's New York where jazz, dance clubs and new fashion trends are sweeping the city. Crime is also running rampant and gangs have taken over the city and are defying prohibition. To avoid jail, you and your gang have been forced to turn informants on the city's most notorious and elusive mob boss. You have gained access to his hidden Speakeasy where you must find the evidence that will lead to his arrest.
